## Architecture

### Backend (Node.js + TypeScript, Surface runner)

**Service:** Express app compiled with `tsc`, run as a Surface-registered service on a loopback port. Bridged to `api.michaelwegter.com/adverteyes/...` via Flask bridge blueprint. `TOMTOM_API_KEY` stored in `.env` on the Surface.

**Database:** SQLite via `better-sqlite3` (sync driver, simplest for Surface). Seeded with 20+ realistic OOH inventory records, 5 clients, 8 campaigns, 15+ bookings, 4 demo users.

**Source files (backend, in runner workspace):**
```
package.json
tsconfig.json
.env                           (TOMTOM_API_KEY, JWT_SECRET, PORT)
src/index.ts                   (Express app + route registration + CORS)
src/db.ts                      (better-sqlite3 init + schema + seed)
src/middleware/auth.ts         (JWT verify + role guard factory)
src/routes/auth.ts             (POST /auth/login, GET /auth/me)
src/routes/inventory.ts        (CRUD + availability query)
src/routes/campaigns.ts        (CRUD + booking summary)
src/routes/bookings.ts         (CRUD + conflict check)
src/routes/users.ts            (Admin-only CRUD)
src/routes/weather.ts          (Open-Meteo proxy — server-side, returns parsed risk)
src/routes/traffic.ts          (TomTom proxy — 15-min TTL cache per asset)
```
13 source files. Compiles to `dist/`.

### Frontend (React + TypeScript + Vite)

**Build target:** `../michaelwegter.com/public/demos/adverteyes/`
**Vite config:** `base: '/demos/adverteyes/'`

**Source files (frontend, in `upwork-runs/adverteyes/demo-src/`):**
```
package.json
vite.config.ts
tsconfig.json
index.html
src/main.tsx                   (CSS imports incl. leaflet/dist/leaflet.css + leaflet icon fix)
src/App.tsx                    (router + ProtectedRoute)
src/contexts/AuthContext.tsx   (user + token state, axios default header)
src/api/index.ts               (axios instance, all typed API calls)
src/leaflet-config.ts          (icon fix — imported once in main.tsx before any map)
src/pages/Login.tsx            (4 demo credential cards, JWT → localStorage)
src/pages/Dashboard.tsx        (KPI tiles + occupancy chart + activity feed)
src/pages/Inventory.tsx        (table/map toggle, Leaflet map, asset detail panel w/ weather + traffic)
src/pages/Campaigns.tsx        (campaign list + detail/booking panel)
src/pages/Bookings.tsx         (booking table + create form + conflict badge)
src/pages/Weather.tsx          (location dropdown, 3-day forecast, install-risk alert)
src/pages/Users.tsx            (Admin-only: table + create/edit/deactivate)
src/components/Layout.tsx      (sidebar + topbar shell, role-aware nav)
src/components/DataTable.tsx   (reusable sort/filter/paginate table)
src/components/KpiCard.tsx
src/components/RoleBadge.tsx
src/components/Modal.tsx
```
22 source files. Exceeds ~12 soft cap — justified at richness 10/10 for a real full-stack multi-page app. Builder must note this in build report.

