## Feature boundary

### Hero: Campaign Operations Dashboard (multi-view)

- **Dashboard** — KPI tiles: Total Inventory Units, Occupancy Rate (%), Active Campaigns, Revenue MTD. Recharts sparkline trend. Quick-action buttons.
- **Inventory** — Filterable table (type / status / search). Columns: name, type, location, size, rate/mo, status badge (available/booked/maintenance). Map toggle: Leaflet/OSM with custom-colored markers by status. Click marker or row = detail panel (weather + traffic data for that asset).
- **Campaigns** — Campaign list (client, dates, budget, % inventory booked). Click = detail with linked inventory units + booking timeline.
- **Bookings** — Full booking table (campaign, unit, date range, rate, status). Create booking form with live conflict check (API validates and returns conflict detail if dates/unit overlap).

### Supporting 1: Weather + Install Risk + Traffic Intelligence

**Weather (Open-Meteo, proxied via backend):**
- Location dropdown (populated from inventory lat/lng in DB)
- 3-day hourly forecast: temperature, wind speed, wind gusts, precipitation, weather_code, visibility
- Install Risk badge: `HIGH` if `precipitation > 0.5mm/h OR wind_speed_10m > 25 mph OR wind_gusts_10m > 35 mph`
- `visibility` shown as "Audience Visibility" metric (low visibility = reduced impression quality — domain-accurate)
- Risk propagates to Bookings view: warning icon on upcoming install dates under weather risk

**Traffic (TomTom Flow API, proxied + cached via backend):**
- Backend caches per-asset, 15-min TTL (stay well inside 2,500 req/day free quota)
- Traffic Score = `((freeFlowSpeed - currentSpeed) / freeFlowSpeed) * 100` = congestion percentage
- Map marker fill-opacity scales with congestion (dark red = heavy traffic = more dwell time = higher effective CPM)
- Asset detail panel: "Traffic Score", current vs. free-flow speed, confidence, road closure flag
- OOH relevance framing: "Heavy congestion near this billboard increases audience dwell time and effective ad impressions"

### Supporting 2: User + Role Management

- **Login** — 4 seeded demo credential cards shown on login page (one-click fill)
- **Protected routes** — Admin: all pages; Sales: hides Users; Ops: Inventory + Bookings + Weather; Client-viewer: Campaigns (own campaigns only, filtered server-side)
- **Users page** (Admin only) — Table of users; edit role dropdown; deactivate toggle; create new user form

