## Database seed (industry-accurate data)

**Inventory (20 units, 3 tiers matching OOH CPM reality):**
- 8 static billboards (highway/downtown/suburban):
  - Premium highway 14x48: 55k impressions/wk, $4 CPM, ~$220/wk rate
  - Downtown arterial 10x36: 42k impressions/wk, $5 CPM
- 6 DOOH digital screens (mall, stadium, transit hub):
  - High-traffic hub: 180k impressions/wk, $8 CPM (highest tier — industry-verified)
  - Mall entrance: 95k impressions/wk, $6 CPM
- 6 truckside wraps (city + suburban routes):
  - City route: 28k impressions/wk, $0.85 CPM (industry-low CPM = key selling point vs. competitors)

**Clients (5):** Ford Dealer Group, Metro Health Network, Pepsi Regional, Coastal Credit Union, FitCore Gym

**Campaigns (8):** Mix of active, upcoming, completed. Budget $5k-$80k.

**Bookings (15):** At least one intentional conflict scenario to demo conflict detection.

**Users (4):**
```
admin@adverteyes.com  / Admin123!   → Admin
sarah@adverteyes.com  / Sales123!   → Sales
ops@adverteyes.com    / Ops1234!    → Ops/Installer
client@forddealer.com / Client12!   → Client-viewer
```

